      "wikitext": "<div id=\"infoboxborder\" style=\"float:right;display:block;\">\n{| \n|-\n| \n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|'''Barn'''\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|'''Big Barn'''\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|'''Deluxe Barn'''\n|-\n|\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|[[File:Barn.png|96px]]\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|[[File:Big Barn.png|96px]]\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|[[File:Deluxe Barn.png|96px]]\n|-\n|colspan=\"4\" id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: center;\"|Information\n|-\n|id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align:right;\"|Upgrades From\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|N/A\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|Barn\n|Big Barn\n|-\n|id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align:right;\"|Building Cost\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|{{Price|6000}}\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|{{Price|12000}}\n|{{Price|25000}}\n|-style=\"vertical-align:top;\"\n|id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align:right;\"|Building Materials\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|{{Name|Wood|350}}{{Name|Stone|150}}\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|{{Name|Wood|450}}{{Name|Stone|200}}\n|{{Name|Wood|550}}{{Name|Stone|300}}\n|-\n|id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align:right;\"|Capacity\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|4\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|8\n|12\n|-style=\"vertical-align:top;\"\n|id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align:right;\"|Animals\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|{{Name|White Cow|link=Cow}}{{Name|Ostrich}}\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|{{Name|White Cow|link=Cow}}{{Name|Goat}}{{Name|Ostrich}}\n|{{Name|White Cow|link=Cow}}{{Name|Goat}}{{Name|Sheep}}{{Name|Pig}}{{Name|Ostrich}}\n|-\n|id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align:right;\"|Footprint\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|'''7x4'''<br />[[File:Marker4x7.png]]\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|'''7x4'''<br />[[File:Marker4x7.png]]\n|'''7x4'''<br />[[File:Marker4x7.png]]\n|-style=\"vertical-align:top;\"\n|id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align:right;\"|Features\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|\n* [[Hay Hopper]]\n* Feeding Bench\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|\n* [[Hay Hopper]]\n* Feeding Bench\n* Enables Pregnancy\n|\n* [[Hay Hopper]]\n* Feeding Bench\n* Enables Pregnancy\n* Autofeed System\n|}</div>\nThe '''Barn''' is a type of [[Carpenter's Shop#Farm Buildings|farm building]] purchasable and upgradeable from [[Robin]] at the [[Carpenter's Shop]].\n\n==Construction==\nThe Barn takes three days to initially construct. During this time, Robin is unreachable for [[Friendship|dialogue or gifting]].\n\nUpgrading the Barn requires two days. During this time, the barn can be used as normal. [[Robin]] can be found inside the Barn for purposes such as [[Friendship|dialogue or gifting]].\n\nThe total cost of a Deluxe Barn, built from scratch, is {{Price|43000}} {{Name|Wood|1350|class=inline}} {{Name|Stone|650|class=inline}}; or, if all wood and stone are bought from Robin during year 1, {{Price|69500}}, and {{Price|175500}} if bought in year 2+.\n\n==Features==\nThe barn houses [[cow]]s, [[goat]]s, [[sheep]], [[pig]]s, and [[ostrich]]es. Once you have unlocked an animal by building the barn needed to house it, that animal can be placed in any other non-upgraded barns you have built as well.\n\n[[Animals#Barn Animals|Barn Animals]] may be stuck outside at night if the barn doors are closed.  The conditions for this are not clear (see [[Animals#Animals Trapped Outside|Animals trapped outside]]). If an animal is stuck outside the barn at night, the next day their mood will be \"grumpy.\" Animals stuck outside are also subject to [[Animals#Wild Animal Attacks|Wild Animal Attacks]].\n\nThe Barn can also be used in a manner similar to the [[Shed]] for storing [[Chest|Chests]], [[Crafting#Artisan Equipment|Artisan Equipment]], [[Furniture]], etc.. The animals are undisturbed by the clutter, even if their paths are blocked.\n\n<gallery>\nanimal left outside dialog.png\n</gallery>\n\n==Bugs==\nIt is possible to have 13 animals in a barn at once, if the player has a barn filled with 11 animals and an existing animal gives birth the same night as an [[Ostrich Egg]] hatches.\n\n==Interior==\n<gallery>\nFile:Barn Interior.png|Barn Interior\nFile:Big Barn Interior.png|Big Barn Interior\nFile:Deluxe Barn Interior.png|Deluxe Barn Interior\n</gallery>\n\n{{NavboxBuildings}}\n\n[[Category:Farm buildings]]\n\n[[de:Stall]]\n[[es:Establo]]\n[[fr:Grange]]\n[[it:Granaio]]\n[[ja:家畜小屋]]\n[[ko:외양간]]\n[[hu:Istálló]]\n[[pt:Celeiro]]\n[[ru:Хлев]]\n[[tr:Ahır]]\n[[zh:畜棚]]"
    }
